
Candidate to Interview Rate = [Interview CNT]/[New CNT]

-- Measure with format forces through formula:
Candidate to Interview Rate = FORMAT([Interview CNT]/[New CNT],"0.00%")

-- There is another way to convert the value into % in Power BI Desktop.
-- Create a measure with simple Divide formula
-- Click on the name of measure in FIELDS section
-- Go to Modeling tab and select % sign in Formatting section
-- The field will automatically be converted to % value.

